{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the area, there is a legend that a girl with purple eyes will have magical powers by the age of 10.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is the story of a little witch who uses her mysterious powers to control a golem and search for a \u201ctreasure\u201d in the depths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941230/extras/explanation_STORY.png?t=1731855668\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It was Charois' 10th birthday.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">She found hherself in an empty, dangerous basement where traps and suspicious shadows awaited her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Charois cannot remember what happened before she came here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The only thing she remembers is that she was told that she would reach the deepest level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The adventure to find the \u201ctreasure\u201d in the depths begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941230/extras/explanation_ABOUT.png?t=1731855668\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is an action RPG in which Charois, a small witch, goes underground with her golem.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use skills and items to get to the deepest underground safely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941230/extras/explanation_FEATURES.png?t=1731855668\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Memory and Action</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dangerous traps lurk in the ground.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use dowsing to see through and instantly remember what is under the ground, and avoid hazards by relying on your memory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">However, traps are not the only obstacle in your search. Pay attention to the approaching shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941230/extras/ex_00.png?t=1731855668\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Skill and Item</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The more you explore, the more mysterious powers are enhanced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the underground more safely by making good use of the skills and items that are released.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Piece-System can boost various stats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It is up to you to decide which abilities you will rely on to fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941230/extras/ex_01_En.png?t=1731855668\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Event Scene</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you progress to the lower levels of the basement, you will be able to retrieve Charois\u2019 memories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When all the memories are retrieved and her reach the deepest level of the basement, what awaits her is either treasure or ......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941230/extras/ex_02_En.png?t=1731855668\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game has multiple endings, but there are no normal, bad, or true endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>I respect all players' choices.</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941230/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731855668","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941230/page.bg.jpg?t=1731855668","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941230/224f79077b7e01dbcd39e7ee1af8dcdae91ee038/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731855668","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_it