 the ground.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use dowsing to see through and instantly remember what is under the ground, and avoid hazards by relying on your memory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">However, traps are not the only obstacle in your search. Pay attention to the approaching shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941230/extras/ex_00.png?t=1731855668\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Skill and Item</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The more you explore, the more mysterious powers are enhanced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the underground more safely by making good use of the skills and items that are released.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Piece-System can boost various stats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It is up to you to decide which abilities you will rely on to fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941230/extras/ex_01_En.png?t=1731855668\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Event Scene</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you progress to the lower levels of the basement, you will be able to retrieve Charois\u2019 memories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When all the memories are retrieved and her reach the deepest level of the basement, what awaits her is either treasure or ......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2941230/extras/ex_02_En.png?t=1731855668\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game has multiple endings, but there are no normal, bad, or true endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>I respect all players' choices.</strong></p>","developers":["\u4e09\u6728\u3088\u3093\u305f"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akam